    /// # Summary
    /// Restricts an operation to an array of indices of a register, i.e., a subregister.
    /// The modifier 'CA' indicates that the operation is controllable and adjointable.
    ///
    /// # Input
    /// ## op
    /// Operation to be restricted to a subregister.
